Ronald Edwards (born September 4, 1964) is a game designer, theorist, and an influential member of the indie role-playing game community. Notably, he is the creator of the Sorcerer RPG, the GNS Theory of gameplay, and The Big Model. Edwards is also co-founder of The Forge, an online community to support Indie RPG design and publication.  
